settings.description:
Travel through the full and scenic views of the plains!
There's many secrets hidden!
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is the Desert Lake; it goes straight to the deserts underground bunker.
The next level is the larry's castle,enjoy.
Dodge the bullets, Touch the snake Corners, and defeat Lemmy, He has more lives and resistance to fire than ever before. Good luck defeating Lemmy and finding the secret exit!
Munchers and nipper plants are alive and happily active here.
Ice, munchers, flurries, penguins, and... shoes?! seems like this wild combo is something that's a bit toooo chill to exist, but it does!
